# AdvancedChat
### Premium Minecraft Chat Management Plugin

[![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/version-2.0-orange?style=for-the-badge&logo=minecraft)](#)
[![Minecraft](https://img.shields.io/badge/minecraft-1.17--1.21-green?style=for-the-badge)](#)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-Premium-red?style=for-the-badge)](#)
[![Discord](https://img.shields.io/badge/discord-Join-5865F2?style=for-the-badge&logo=discord)](https://discord.gg/advancedchat)

*The most advanced, feature-rich chat plugin for your Minecraft server.*

</div>

---

## 📦 Features

### 💬 Chat Channels
- **Local** — Only nearby players can see your message
- **Global** — Server-wide chat
- **Staff** — Private channel for staff members
- **Owner** — Exclusive channel for server owners
- Configurable range and permissions per channel

### 🔨 Moderation
- `/mute`, `/unmute`, `/ban`, `/unban`, `/kick`, `/warn`, `/freeze`
- Auto-mute and auto-ban based on warning thresholds
- Player notes system
- Full message history

### 📊 Report System
- Players report others with `/report <player> <reason>`
- Staff view all reports in an interactive **GUI menu**
- Click a report to open the target's staff menu directly
- Reports saved to `reports.json` — persists through restarts
- `/reportclear [player]` to remove reports

### 🤖 Chat Bot
- Keyword-based auto-responses — no unwanted spam
- Supports **5 game modes**: Survival, Skyblock, Factions, Prison, RPG
- Configurable via `bot.yml`

### 🎨 Chat Colors
- `/acolor` — Interactive color picker GUI
- Full gradient support
- Per-permission color unlocks

### 🔒 Anti-Spam & Caps Filter
- Automatically blocks repeated messages
- Caps lock filter with configurable threshold
- Slow mode support

### 📩 Private Messaging
- `/msg <player> <message>` — Send a private message
- `/r <message>` — Quick reply

### 👮 Staff Tools
- Full-featured **Staff Menu GUI**
- `/stafflist` — View all online staff
- **Chat Spy** — Monitor all channels silently

### 📢 MOTD
- Custom join messages based on player rank

### ⚙️ Storage
- **JSON** — Zero-setup, works out of the box
- **MySQL** — For larger servers, fully configurable

### 🌐 Multi-Language
- English, Turkish, Spanish — fully translated
- Every single message is customizable via `lang/` files

---

## 🔗 Dependencies

| Dependency | Type |
|---|---|
| [Vault](https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/vault.34315/) | **Required** |
| [LuckPerms](https://luckperms.net/) | Optional |
| [PlaceholderAPI](https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/placeholderapi.6245/) | Optional |

---

## 📋 Commands & Permissions

### Chat
| Command | Description | Permission |
|---|---|---|
| `/global [msg]` | Switch to / send in Global channel | `advancedchat.global` |
| `/local [msg]` | Switch to / send in Local channel | `advancedchat.local` |
| `/msg <player> <msg>` | Send a private message | `advancedchat.msg` |
| `/r <msg>` | Reply to last private message | `advancedchat.msg` |
| `/acolor` | Open chat color picker GUI | `advancedchat.color` |
| `/mention` | Mention a player | `advancedchat.mention` |

### Moderation
| Command | Description | Permission |
|---|---|---|
| `/mute <player> [reason]` | Mute a player | `advancedchat.mute` |
| `/unmute <player>` | Unmute a player | `advancedchat.mute` |
| `/ban <player> [reason]` | Ban a player from chat | `advancedchat.ban` |
| `/unban <player>` | Unban a player | `advancedchat.ban` |
| `/kick <player> [reason]` | Kick a player | `advancedchat.kick` |
| `/warn <player> [reason]` | Warn a player | `advancedchat.warn` |
| `/freeze <player>` | Freeze a player | `advancedchat.freeze` |
| `/clearchat` | Clear the chat | `advancedchat.clearchat` |

### Staff & Reports
| Command | Description | Permission |
|---|---|---|
| `/report <player> <reason>` | Report a player | `advancedchat.report` |
| `/reportlist` | View all reports (GUI) | `advancedchat.reportlist` |
| `/reportclear [player]` | Clear reports | `advancedchat.reportclear` |
| `/stafflist` | View online staff | `advancedchat.stafflist` |

### General
| Command | Description | Permission |
|---|---|---|
| `/ac reload` | Reload the plugin | `advancedchat.reload` |

---

## ⚙️ Configuration

After the first startup, the following files will be generated in `plugins/AdvancedChat/`:

```
plugins/AdvancedChat/
├── config.yml       — Main configuration
├── bot.yml          — Chat bot keywords & responses
├── reports.json     — Saved player reports
├── data/            — Player data (JSON mode)
└── lang/
    ├── en.yml
    ├── tr.yml
    └── es.yml
```

### MySQL Setup
In `config.yml`, set `storage-type: mysql` and fill in your credentials:

```yaml
storage-type: mysql   # or json

mysql:
  host: localhost
  port: 3306
  database: advancedchat
  username: root
  password: yourpassword
```

### Chat Format
Customize the chat format using placeholders:

```yaml
format:
  local:  "&8[&7Local&8] {prefix}&f{player}&8: &7{message}"
  global: "&8[&aGlobal&8] {prefix}&f{player}&8: &f{message}"
```

---

## 🚀 Installation

1. Download the latest `AdvancedChat.jar` from [Releases](../../releases)
2. Place it in your `plugins/` folder
3. Make sure **Vault** is installed
4. Restart your server
5. Configure `plugins/AdvancedChat/config.yml` as needed
6. Run `/ac reload`

